      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Weekend music listing May 12; performance site noted</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A music listing in Weekend yesterday misidentified the hall where the Bronx Opera Company is presenting Donizetti's ''Don Pasquale'' this weekend. The performance at 8 tonight is at the John Jay College Theater, 899 10th Avenue, at 59th Street, in Manhattan, not at Lehman College in the Bronx.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
